00:04:05.890 --> 00:04:09.650 align:middle line:84%
of spirituality
in the workplace.

00:04:09.650 --> 00:04:11.000 align:middle line:90%
And it's a good move.

00:04:11.000 --> 00:04:14.890 align:middle line:90%
