00:04:14.890 --> 00:04:21.519 align:middle line:84%
>> Well, I took the step due to
a three ring wake up call that

00:04:21.519 --> 00:04:22.990 align:middle line:90%
I had in 1989.

00:04:22.990 --> 00:04:24.198 align:middle line:90%
>> A three ring wake up call?

00:04:24.198 --> 00:04:25.865 align:middle line:84%
>> I call it my three
ring wake up call.

00:04:25.865 --> 00:04:26.710 align:middle line:90%
>> What happened?

00:04:26.710 --> 00:04:29.930 align:middle line:84%
>> Divorce, end of
a 25 year marriage.

00:04:29.930 --> 00:04:30.730 align:middle line:90%
Cancer.

00:04:30.730 --> 00:04:33.130 align:middle line:84%
