shaving one morning.

00:04:33.130 --> 00:04:35.070 align:middle line:90%
And they took it out.

00:04:35.070 --> 00:04:36.940 align:middle line:90%
And I had radiation.

00:04:36.940 --> 00:04:40.120 align:middle line:84%
