officer came in and said, Tom,

00:04:43.300 --> 00:04:45.160 align:middle line:90%
our credit line's exhausted.

00:04:45.160 --> 00:04:48.070 align:middle line:84%
And we're $1 million
short on the bank account.

00:04:48.070 --> 00:04:51.500 align:middle line:84%
All three of those things
happened within four months

00:04:51.500 --> 00:04:52.300 align:middle line:90%
in 1989.

00:04:52.300 --> 00:04:53.752 align:middle line:90%
>> Wow.

00:04:53.752 --> 00:04:56.180 align:middle line:84%
>> And those are the three
major wake up calls that happen

00:04:56.180 --> 00:04:57.400 align:middle line:90%
in our lives.

00:04:57.400 --> 00:05:00.800 align:middle line:84%
Love relationship,
health, and career.

00:05:00.800 --> 00:05:03.150 align:middle line:84%
And all three of
those happened to me.

00:05:03.150 --> 00:05:04.810 align:middle line:84%
