and determined,

00:05:19.690 --> 00:05:21.650 align:middle line:90%
I need a different game plan.

00:05:21.650 --> 00:05:23.220 align:middle line:84%
So out of that
came this game plan

00:05:23.220 --> 00:05:25.360 align:middle line:84%
that I developed over
the last 10 years

00:05:25.360 --> 00:05:26.950 align:middle line:90%
in winning in the game of life.

00:05:26.950 --> 00:05:30.520 align:middle line:84%
>> There is a phrase in your
book that resonates with me.

00:05:30.520 --> 00:05:36.530 align:middle line:84%
You referred to working out and
working in and the differences.

00:05:36.530 --> 00:05:37.640 align:middle line:90%
I love that.

00:05:37.640 --> 00:05:39.620 align:middle line:84%
And I'd love to hear
you talk about it.

00:05:39.620 --> 00:05:42.710 align:middle line:90%
>> Well, that was not my phrase.

00:05:42.710 --> 00:05:49.350 align:middle line:84%
