00:05:56.570 --> 00:05:57.770 align:middle line:90%
I said, no.

00:05:57.770 --> 00:05:58.880 align:middle line:90%
I really haven't had time.

00:05:58.880 --> 00:06:00.060 align:middle line:90%
I've been working out a lot.

00:06:00.060 --> 00:06:01.768 align:middle line:84%
In other words, I was
playing basketball.

00:06:01.768 --> 00:06:03.268 align:middle line:84%
I said, I've been
working out a lot,

00:06:03.268 --> 00:06:05.370 align:middle line:84%
but I haven't had a
chance to do my tai chi.

00:06:05.370 --> 00:06:10.310 align:middle line:84%
He looked at me and
said, working out,

00:06:10.310 --> 00:06:14.500 align:middle line:90%
as opposed to working in.

00:06:14.500 --> 00:06:15.560 align:middle line:90%
Busted.

00:06:15.560 --> 00:06:16.400 align:middle line:90%
>> Busted.

00:06:16.400 --> 00:06:17.330 align:middle line:90%
>> Big time.

00:06:17.330 --> 00:06:18.410 align:middle line:90%
>> Busted.

00:06:18.410 --> 00:06:22.490 align:middle line:84%
>> So that meant I was
still, at that point,

00:06:22.490 --> 00:06:27.320 align:middle line:84%
engaged in intellectual
pursuits, working out,

00:06:27.320 --> 00:06:31.310 align:middle line:84%
