really going inside.

00:06:31.310 --> 00:06:33.950 align:middle line:84%
>> I hope you're aware of
the gifts that you pass

00:06:33.950 --> 00:06:35.630 align:middle line:90%
on to the world.

00:06:35.630 --> 00:06:38.390 align:middle line:84%
Because, for example,
that's a phrase

00:06:38.390 --> 00:06:42.483 align:middle line:84%
that I will remember and
use for the rest of my life.

00:06:42.483 --> 00:06:44.400 align:middle line:84%
>> I pass it on and got
it from somebody else.

00:06:44.400 --> 00:06:45.500 align:middle line:84%
I think that's what
it's all about.

00:06:45.500 --> 00:06:46.430 align:middle line:90%
>> Precisely.

00:06:46.430 --> 00:06:47.270 align:middle line:90%
>> Learning and teaching.

00:06:47.270 --> 00:06:48.230 align:middle line:90%
Learning and teaching.

00:06:48.230 --> 00:06:49.350 align:middle line:90%
>> Precisely.

00:06:49.350 --> 00:06:50.150 align:middle line:90%
>> Thank you.

00:06:50.150 --> 00:06:50.950 align:middle line:90%
>> Precisely.

00:06:50.950 --> 00:06:53.930 align:middle line:84%
It's just a wonderful
aspect of it.

00:06:53.930 --> 00:06:55.700 align:middle line:84%
Were there people
in your life, as you

00:06:55.700 --> 00:07:00.740 align:middle line:84%
