that is incredible.

00:08:07.070 --> 00:08:10.640 align:middle line:84%
>> You know what's striking to
me about this as well is when I

00:08:10.640 --> 00:08:12.600 align:middle line:84%
hear you speak
this way, I'm very,

00:08:12.600 --> 00:08:17.250 align:middle line:84%
very impressed to hear a man,
and a powerful man speaking

00:08:17.250 --> 00:08:18.050 align:middle line:90%
that way.

00:08:18.050 --> 00:08:22.370 align:middle line:84%
Because so often people
have thought over the years,

00:08:22.370 --> 00:08:24.060 align:middle line:84%
this is very much
a woman's world,

00:08:24.060 --> 00:08:26.450 align:middle line:84%
the idea of spirituality,
