examples for other men,

00:08:38.330 --> 00:08:40.250 align:middle line:90%
it's remarkable.

00:08:40.250 --> 00:08:44.120 align:middle line:84%
I'd like to hear you talk
about how you have affected

00:08:44.120 --> 00:08:46.290 align:middle line:90%
other men in this business.

00:08:46.290 --> 00:08:48.740 align:middle line:84%
>> First of all, I want to
credit those I've learned from.

00:08:48.740 --> 00:08:52.050 align:middle line:84%
And I've learned from women
who've run with the wolves.

00:08:52.050 --> 00:08:52.850 align:middle line:90%
>> Oh, yes.

00:08:52.850 --> 00:08:56.570 align:middle line:84%
>> And probably of
my personal mentors,

00:08:56.570 --> 00:09:02.310 align:middle line:84%
