you who is just all-male--

00:09:45.510 --> 00:09:46.310 align:middle line:90%
>> Thank you.

00:09:46.310 --> 00:09:47.110 align:middle line:90%
>> You're welcome.

00:09:47.110 --> 00:09:49.430 align:middle line:90%
You're just a guy's guy.

00:09:49.430 --> 00:09:52.800 align:middle line:84%
And to see you setting
that example is remarkable.

00:09:52.800 --> 00:09:57.230 align:middle line:84%
So do you see differences in
corporate America, in men?

00:09:57.230 --> 00:10:00.860 align:middle line:84%
And I know it's almost a
question that makes you shy.

00:10:00.860 --> 00:10:04.440 align:middle line:84%
But I'd love to hear you
talk about it, because it

00:10:04.440 --> 00:10:05.620 align:middle line:90%
is what it is.

00:10:05.620 --> 00:10:06.420 align:middle line:90%
>> OK.

00:10:06.420 --> 00:10:09.300 align:middle line:84%
Let's talk about who I
maybe had a good fortune

00:10:09.300 --> 00:10:11.050 align:middle line:90%
to affect in recent years.

00:10:11.050 --> 00:10:11.850 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes.

00:10:11.850 --> 00:10:14.220 align:middle line:90%
>> Up until now.

00:10:14.220 --> 00:10:23.460 align:middle line:84%
