each of these elements.

00:20:28.343 --> 00:20:30.010 align:middle line:84%
Because the bad news
is, everybody says,

00:20:30.010 --> 00:20:31.520 align:middle line:90%
what's the secret to success?

00:20:31.520 --> 00:20:33.610 align:middle line:84%
The bad news is,
there's a ton of them.

