with family and friends.

00:21:40.910 --> 00:21:46.240 align:middle line:84%
The fourth is to share it
in my business organization.

00:21:46.240 --> 00:21:47.380 align:middle line:90%
Not shoulds.

00:21:47.380 --> 00:21:48.670 align:middle line:90%
Not oughtas.

00:21:48.670 --> 00:21:50.860 align:middle line:84%
By the way, you won't find
the word should, oughta,

00:21:50.860 --> 00:21:53.200 align:middle line:84%
