in that book,

00:21:53.200 --> 00:21:56.060 align:middle line:84%
or anywhere in anything
in our company.

00:21:56.060 --> 00:21:57.940 align:middle line:90%
It's serving it up buffet style.

00:21:57.940 --> 00:22:02.420 align:middle line:84%
So sharing this in our business
organization is the next.

00:22:02.420 --> 00:22:05.155 align:middle line:84%
And then the next
evolution outward

00:22:05.155 --> 00:22:10.180 align:middle line:84%
